# Istok, Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Istok () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 262 as of 2010. There are 6 streets.
Geography
Istok is located 39&nbsp;km northwest of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Istomino is the nearest rural locality.
